                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200918-131-off760 t18200918-131-cd761"></join>, one watch, value 5 l.; one seal, value 1 l.; one ring, value 2 s., and one ribbon, value 1 d., the goods of 
                     
